'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales na fargabar nuna kansu a matsayin 'yan wasa
Wasu 'yan majalisa sun nuna rashin amincewarsu game da shawarar sauya taken su zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan shawara ta samo asali ne daga shirin da ake yi na sauya sunan majalisa zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
'Yan majalisa daga ko'ina cikin siyasa suna damuwa cewa wannan zai zama abin dariya.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Labour ya ce jam'iyyarsa na damuwa cewa "za ta iya yin waƙa da Twp da Pwp".
Ga masu karatu da ba sa zama a Wales: A yaren Welsh, twp na nufin wawa kuma pwp na nufin kura.
Wani memba na Majalisar Plaid ya ce kungiyar gabaɗaya "ba ta da farin ciki" kuma ya ba da shawarar wasu hanyoyin.
Wani memba na Jam'iyyar Conservative ta Wales ya ce yana buɗe  ga canjin sunan, amma ya jaddada cewa kawai ƙaramin magana ne ya raba MWP daga Muppet (farkawa).
A wannan yanayin, ana furta harafin W a yaren Welsh kamar yadda ake furta harafin U a yaren Yorkshire.
Kwamitin majalisar, wanda a halin yanzu yake shirin gabatar da sauye-sauyen sunaye, ya ce: "Hukumar karshe game da duk wani bayanin yadda za a kira 'yan majalisar za ta kasance batun tattaunawa ne ga 'yan majalisar".
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba wa majalisa na Wales damar canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta wallafa sakamakon wani taron jama'a kan shawarwarin, wanda ya nuna goyon baya mai yawa ga taron majalisar dokokin Wales.
A game da sunan 'yan majalisa, Hukumar ta fi son 'yan majalisa na Welsh ko WMP, amma an fi amincewa da zaɓin MWP a cikin wani taron jama'a.
A bayyane yake cewa jam'iyyun MLA suna ba da shawarwari game da wasu zaɓuɓɓuka, amma matsalolin da ke tattare da cimma yarjejeniya na iya zama ciwo ga Shugaba Elin Jones, wanda ya gabatar da wani tsari na doka game da canje-canje a cikin 'yan makonni.
Dokar sauye-sauyen za ta hada da wasu canje-canje ga yadda majalisa ke aiki, ciki har da dokokin da suka shafi cire 'yan majalisar da kuma tsarin kwamitocin.
MF za su yi kuri'ar ƙarshe game da sunayensu yayin tattaunawar dokar.
