Shugaban Macedonia Gjorge Ivanov, wanda ya yi adawa da kuri'ar raba gardamar da aka yi game da sauya sunan, ya ce ba zai yi la'akari da sakamakon zaben ba.
Sai dai magoya bayan zaben, ciki har da Firaministan kasar Zoran Zaev, sun ce sauya sunan kawai farashin shiga Tarayyar Turai da NATO ne.
