Wani ɗan shekara 13 ya ji rauni a cikin wani kifi a California
Majiyoyin ruwa sun ce wani kifi mai suna shark ya kai hari kuma ya ji wa wani yaro dan shekara 13 rauni yayin da yake ruwa yana neman lobster a California a ranar Asabar a ranar farko ta kakar lobster.
An kai harin ne da misalin karfe 7 na safe kusa da Beacon's Beach a Encinitas.
Chad Hammel ya shaida wa gidan talabijin na KSWB-TV a San Diego cewa ya yi ninkaya da wasu abokansa a cikin ruwa na rabin sa'a a safiyar Asabar lokacin da ya ji wani yaro yana ihu kuma ya yi iyo zuwa gare shi tare da wasu mutane don fitar da shi daga ruwa.
Hammel ya fara tunanin cewa kawai yana farin ciki ne saboda kama wani lobster amma sai ya fahimci cewa yaron yana ihu "An cije ni!"
An cije ni!'
An yi wa ƙashin ƙugu duka, ya ce ya lura da Hammel bayan ya kai ga yaron.
"Na yi ihu ga kowa ya fito daga cikin ruwa, 'Akwai kifi a cikin ruwa!' " in ji Hammel.
An kai yaron a kan jirgi mai saukar ungulu zuwa asibitin Rady Children's Hospital da ke San Diego, inda aka kwantar da shi cikin mawuyacin hali.
Ba a san irin kifin da ya kai harin ba.
Kyaftin Larry Giles ya bayyana a wata sanarwa da ya yi wa manema labarai cewa an ga wani kifi a yankin makonni da suka gabata amma an ce ba shi da haɗari.
Giles ya kara da cewa wanda aka kashe ya ji rauni a cikin kirji.
Hukumomi sun hana kowa shiga bakin rairayin bakin teku daga Ponto Beach a Casablad zuwa Swami's a Ecinitas na tsawon awanni 48 don dalilai na bincike da tsaro.
Giles ya ce akwai nau'in kifi fiye da 135 a yankin, amma yawancin ba su da haɗari.
Sainsbury's na shirin kara bunkasa kasuwar kayayyakin kwalliya a Burtaniya
Sainsbury's na kalubalantar Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams da ke da wuraren da aka keɓe don kayan kwalliyar kantin sayar da kayayyaki da aka ba da mataimakan ƙwararru
A wani bangare na gagarumin ci gaba da kasuwar kayayyakin kwalliya ta Burtaniya mai darajar fam biliyan 2.8, wadda ke ci gaba da bunkasa yayin da tallace-tallace a masana'antar kera kayayyaki da kayan gida ke raguwa, za a fara gwajin manyan layukan kayayyakin kwalliya a shaguna 11 a kasar, kuma za a fara amfani da su a wasu shaguna a shekara mai zuwa idan sun yi nasara.
Ƙarin kuɗi a cikin kayan ado yana faruwa ne a lokacin da manyan kantuna ke neman sababbin hanyoyin da za su yi amfani da sararin da aka yi amfani da shi don talabijin, microwave, da kayayyakin gida.
Sainsbury's ta ce za ta ninka girman kayan kwalliyarta zuwa kayayyaki 3,000, gami da a karon farko alamun kamar Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da Dr. PawPaw.
L'Oreal, Maybelline da Burt's Bees za su yi amfani da sarari da yawa tare da wuraren da aka yi amfani da su kamar yadda ake samu a shaguna kamar Boots.
Har ila yau, babban kanti yana sake sabunta kayan kwalliyarsa na Boutique don yawancin kayayyakin su zama masu cin ganyayyaki - ingancin da matasa masu sayayya ke buƙata.
Bugu da ƙari, mai sayar da turare The Fragrance Shop zai gwada izini a shagunan Sainsbury's biyu, na farko daga cikinsu ya buɗe a Croydon, a kudancin London yayin da na biyu zai buɗe a Selly Oak, Birmingham, daga baya a cikin shekara.
Kasuwancin kan layi da kuma sauyawa zuwa sayen ƙananan kayan abinci a kowace rana daga ƙananan shagunan unguwa sun tilasta manyan kantuna su yi aiki sosai don shawo kan mutane su saya daga gare su.
Mike Coupe, babban manajan kamfanin sayar da kayayyaki na Sainsbury's, ya ce wuraren sayar da kayayyaki za su zama kamar manyan kantuna yayin da manyan kantunan ke ƙoƙarin tsayayya da ragi kamar Aldi da Lidl ta hanyar ba da ƙarin ayyuka da kayayyakin da ba abinci ba.
Sainsbury's ya gabatar da kantunan Argos a daruruwan shaguna kuma ya kuma gabatar da gidaje da yawa tun lokacin da ya sayi sarƙoƙin biyu kimanin shekaru biyu da suka gabata, kuma wannan dabarar ta ba da tallace-tallace na abinci kuma ya sa sayayya ta fi riba.
Ƙoƙarin da babban kanti ya yi a dā na sake gyara kayan kwalliya da kuma magunguna bai yi nasara ba.
Sainsbury's ya yi ƙoƙari ya haɗa kai da Boots a farkon 2000s amma haɗin gwiwa ya ƙare a cikin takaddama game da raba kudaden shiga daga kantin sayar da magunguna a cikin manyan kantuna.
An yi amfani da wannan sabuwar dabarar ne bayan da kamfanin sayar da magunguna na Sainsbury's ya sayar da shagonsa na 281 shekaru uku da suka gabata ga Celesio, mai kamfanin Lloyds Pharmacy, a kan fam miliyan 125.
An shirya Lloyds ya taka rawa a cikin shirin, tare da ƙarawa a cikin shaguna huɗu da ke da samfuran samfuran kayan kwalliya, gami da La Roche-Posay da Vichy.
Paul Mills-Hicks, babban jami'in kasuwanci a Sainsbury's ya ce: "Mun sauya siffar sassanmu na kayan kwalliya don inganta yanayin abokan cinikinmu.
Mun kuma saka hannun jari a cikin abokan aiki da aka horar da su musamman waɗanda za su kasance a shirye su ba da shawara.
An tsara jerinmu don biyan kowane buƙata kuma yanayi mai ban sha'awa da wurare masu kyau sun sa mu zama kyakkyawan makoma don kayan kwalliya, sabanin tsohuwar hanyar cin kasuwa".
Peter Jones  "mai fushi bayan Holly Willoughby ta yi watsi da yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11
Tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Dragons Den, Peter Jones ya fusata bayan mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen talabijin Holly Willoughby ta janye daga yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11 da alamar sa ta zamani don mayar da hankali kan sabbin yarjejeniyoyin ta da Marks da Spencer da ITV
Willoughby ba shi da lokacinsa don kayan aikin gida da kayan haɗi na Truly.
An kwatanta kasuwancin ma'auratan da alamar Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop.
Mai gabatar da wannan safiyar, mai shekaru 37, ta yi amfani da Instagram don sanar da barin aikinta.
Holly Willoughby ta bar tauraron Dragons Den, Peter Jones, cikin fushi bayan da ta yi murabus daga kasuwancin kasuwancin su a minti na ƙarshe don mai da hankali kan sabbin yarjejeniyoyinsa na musamman tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
Wasu majiyoyi sun ce Jones ya kasance "mai fushi" lokacin da 'yar jaridar ta TV ta yarda a yayin ganawa a hedkwatar masarautar kasuwancin ta a Marlow, Buckinghamshire, cewa sabbin kwangilar ta - wanda ke da darajar fam miliyan 1.5 - ba ta da isasshen lokaci don ba da kanta ga kayan aikin gida da kayan haɗi na Truly.
An kwatanta kasuwancin da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop's Goop kuma an kiyasta cewa zai ninka dukiyar Willoughby, wanda aka kiyasta kusan £ 11 miliyan.
Da zarar Willoughby, mai shekara 37, ya yi amfani da Instagram don sanar da cewa ya bar Truly, Jones ya bar Burtaniya don zuwa ɗaya daga cikin wuraren hutunsa.
Wani majiya ya ce: "Babu shakka, Truly ita ce ta fi muhimmanci a rayuwar Holly.
Dole ne ta kasance makomar ta ta dogon lokaci da za ta sa ta yi aiki na shekaru 20 masu zuwa.
Shawarwarin da ya yanke na barin aikin ya sa duk wanda ya shiga cikin lamarin ya rasa bakin magana.
Babu wanda ya yarda da abin da ke faruwa a ranar Talata, suna kusa da kaddamarwa.
Akwai wani babban kantin sayar da kayayyaki a hedkwatar Marlow, a shirye suke su sayar".
Masana sun yi imanin cewa barin mai gabatar da wannan safiyar, daya daga cikin fitattun taurari a Burtaniya, na iya kashe kamfanin miliyoyin saboda saka hannun jari mai yawa a cikin kayayyaki daga matashin kai da kyandirori zuwa tufafi da kayan gida da kuma yiwuwar jinkiri a ƙaddamar da alama.
Kuma hakan zai iya kawo ƙarshen abokantaka mai tsawo.
Willoughby, mahaifiyar yara uku, da mijinta Dan Baldwin sun kasance abokai da Jones da matarsa Tara Capp har tsawon shekaru goma.
Willoughby ya kirkiro Truly tare da Capp a shekarar 2016 kuma Jones, mai shekaru 52, ya shiga kamfanin a matsayin shugaban a watan Maris.
Ma'aurata suna yin hutu tare kuma Jones yana da kashi 40% na kamfanin samar da talabijin na Baldwin.
Willoughby za ta zama jakada ta M&S kuma za ta maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin baƙo a shirin ITV I'm A Celebrity.
Wani majiya da ke kusa da Jones ya ce a daren jiya "ba ya son yin magana game da harkokin kasuwancinsa".
