Duba, Daniel Sturridge na Liverpool ya tashi da Chelsea
Daniel Sturridge ya ceci Liverpool daga shan kashi a gasar Premier da Chelsea da ci daya a minti na 89 a ranar Asabar a Stamford Bridge a London.
Sturridge ya samu wata gudummawa daga Xherdan Shaqiri yayin da yake kusan mita 25 daga kofar Chelsea, tare da tawagarsa ta sauka 1-0.
Ya buga kwallon hagu kafin ya buga a raga na biyu.
Wannan ƙoƙarin ya wuce saman ƙofar ƙofar yayin da yake juyawa zuwa kusurwar dama ta dama.
Daga karshe kwallon ta fadi a bayan Kepa Arrizabalaga ta shiga raga.
"Kawai na yi kokarin sanya kaina a matsayi, na kai ga kwallon kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq koyaushe suna wasa a gaba kamar yadda zasu iya, don haka na yi kokarin samar da lokaci mai yawa", in ji Sturridge ga LiverpoolFC.com.
"Na ga Kante yana zuwa kuma na yi wasa kuma ban yi tunani sosai ba kuma na yi wasa".
Chelsea ta ci 1-0 a farkon rabin wasan bayan da ta ci kwallo a minti na 25 da tauraruwar Belgium Eden Hazard.
Dan wasan tsakiya na Blue ya wuce Mateo Kovacic kafin ya tashi daga tsakiyar filin kuma ya shiga tsakiyar Liverpool.
Kovacic ya yi gaggawar wucewa a tsakiyar filin wasa.
Sai ya yi wani kyakkyawan motsawa wanda ya kawo Hazard a yankin.
Hazard ya wuce tsaron kuma ya zo kan gungumen na biyu tare da burin hagu a gaban Alisson Becker na Liverpool.
Liverpool za ta fafata da Napoli a wasan farko na gasar zakarun Turai da karfe 3 na yammacin ranar Laraba a filin wasa na Stadio San Paolo da ke Naples, Italiya.
Chelsea za ta fafata da Videoton a gasar Europa League da karfe 3 na yammacin Alhamis a London.
