Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron Brett Kavanaugh
Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar mai neman zama a kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da matar da ta zarge shi da aikata laifin fyade a shekarun 1980s, Christine Blasey Ford.
A halin yanzu, siyasa ta ci gaba da rikici, tare da tashoshin watsa labarai da ke dakatar da shirye-shiryen yau da kullun don juyin juya halin ƙarshe a ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya tsara don FBI ta gudanar da binciken mako guda game da tuhumar.
Ford ta sanar da kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai cewa ta tabbata da cewa Kavanaugh ya taba ta da giya kuma ya yi kokarin cire mata tufafinta a wani biki a makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a lokacin da yake shaida a kan lamarin, ya ce ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila mutane miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ya nuna a ranar Juma'a sun bi shaidar.
Kamfanin yana lissafin matsakaicin masu sauraro akan CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu wannan adadin ba nan da nan ga sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa da suka watsa shi, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen tana da matsala wajen ƙidaya yawan masu sauraro a ofisoshinsa.
Don sanya shi cikin hangen nesa, wannan shine irin masu sauraro kamar wasan kwallon kafa ko kyautar Oscar.
Kafofin watsa labarai na Fox News Channel, wadanda masu bada shawarwari suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, sun jagoranci dukkan cibiyoyin sadarwa, tare da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a yayin sauraron sauraron ranar, Nielsen ya ruwaito.
ABC ita ce cibiyar sadarwa ta biyu tare da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta sami masu kallo miliyan 3.1, NBC miliyan 2.94, MSNBC miliyan 2.89 da CNN miliyan 2.52, a cewar Nielsen.
Har ila, mutane sun ci gaba da son sauraron jawabin.
Flake ne babban jigon wasan kwaikwayon na ranar Juma'a.
Bayan da ofishin Jamhuriyar Republican ya fitar da wata sanarwa da ta ce zai kada kuri'ar Kavanaugh, 'yan jarida na CNN da CBS sun dauki hoton Flake a safiyar ranar Juma'a yayin da masu zanga-zanga ke zaginsa yayin da yake kokarin hawa lif zuwa wani taron Kwamitin Shari'a.
Ya yi ta kallon ƙasa na mintuna da dama yayin da aka tsawata masa kuma aka watsa shi kai tsaye a CNN.
"Ina nan a gabanka", in ji wata mata.
"Kana ganin ina gaya wa kasar gaskiya ne?
An gaya masa cewa, 'Kai mai iko ne, amma mata da yawa ba su da iko.'"
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya bayar da bayanin kuma ya ce kafin a rufe lif din yana da wasu abubuwa da zai ce a lokacin sauraron kwamitin.
Dukkanin gidajen rediyo da kuma tashoshin rediyo sun watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye bayan wasu sa'o'i, lokacin da kwamitin shari'a ya kada kuri'ar gabatar da nadin Kavanaugh ga majalisar dattijai don jefa kuri'a.
Amma Flake ya ce zai yi hakan ne kawai idan ya tabbata cewa FBI za ta bincika tuhume-tuhume da ake yi wa dan takarar a cikin mako mai zuwa, kamar yadda 'yan Democrat suka bukaci.
Flake ya samu tabbacin hakan ne daga tattaunawar da ya yi da abokinsa, Sanata Chris Coons na jam'iyyar Democrat.
Bayan tattaunawa da Coons da wasu sanatoci daga baya, Flake ya yanke shawarar.
Zaɓin Flake yana da mahimmanci, saboda a bayyane yake cewa 'yan Republican ba za su sami kuri'un da za su amince da Kavanaugh ba tare da binciken ba.
Shugaba Trump ya kaddamar da binciken FBI kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh.
