Wutar ƙanƙara tana zubo toka a birnin Mexico
Tashin toka daga dutsen Popocatepetl ya kai kudancin babban birnin Mexico.
Cibiyar Kula da Bala'i ta Kasa ta gargadi 'yan Mexico a ranar Asabar da su guji volcano bayan da aka samu tashin hankali a cikin ramin da ya yi sanadiyar fitar da gas da toka 183 a cikin sa'o'i 24.
Cibiyar ta duba yawan girgizar ƙasa da ta yi.
Hotunan da aka yada a shafukan sada zumunta sun nuna cewa toka ta rufe gilashin mota a unguwannin birnin Mexico kamar Xochimilco.
Masana ilimin kasa sun gano karuwar aiki a dutsen mai fitad da wuta wanda ke da nisan mil 45 (72 kilomita) kudu maso gabashin babban birnin kasar tun lokacin da girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.1 ta afkawa tsakiyar Mexico a watan Satumbar 2017.
Dutsen mai fitad da wuta, wanda aka fi sani da "Don Goyo" yana aiki tun 1994.
