"Babban haɗarin da Rosa ko kuma guguwa za ta iya jawowa shi ne ruwan sama mai yawa a Baja California, arewa maso yammacin Sonora, da kuma kudu maso yammacin hamadar Amirka", in ji National Hurricane Center.
Ana tsammanin irin wannan ruwan sama zai iya haifar da ambaliyar ruwa mai saurin mutuwa da kuma kwararar tarkace a hamada, da kuma ambaliyar ƙasa a kan tsaunuka.
