Idan kana son ka ƙara yawan kayan da kake sakawa a kai ko kuma ka hana rana fita, ka nemi ƙarin bayani.
Masu zanen kaya Valentino da Thom Browne sun bayyana a kan tituna jerin kayan kwalliya masu yawa don tarin su na bazara-rani na 2019 wanda ya burge duniya ta fashion a Paris Fashion Week.
Hatsuna masu banƙyama sun zama ruwan dare a Instagram a wannan bazarar kuma waɗannan masu zanen kaya sun aika da abubuwan da suka kirkira a kan hanya.
