Ya zama al'ada yanzu don neman nassoshi game da Brexit a cikin kowane sabon fim tare da ɗan ɗan Britaniya kuma wannan yana da amfani ga wannan farfadowar wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English, wanda ya fara a 2003 kuma ya sake dawowa a 2011 tare da Johnny English - The Rebirth.
Shin wannan magana ta rashin mutunci game da yadda muke lalata da kanmu za ta zama sabuwar damar fitar da kayayyaki ta kasar?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny English mara iya magana da fuskar roba da idanu daga cikin orbit ya sami lasisinsa don rushe abubuwa a karo na biyu - kuma sunansa ya nuna fiye da kowane abu cewa wannan abu ne mai ban dariya wanda aka tsara don ƙasashen da ba su da harshen Turanci.
