Amurka na iya amfani da Sojojin Ruwa don aiwatar da  toshewa  da hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida
Washington na iya, idan ya cancanta, ta yi amfani da sojan ruwanta don hana samar da makamashi na Rasha a kasuwa, gami da na Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya ce shigar da Rasha cikin Syria - musamman ma inda take aiki a gayyatar gwamnatin da ta dace - wata hujja ce ta gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
Ina ganin dalilin da yasa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shine saboda suna son yin sulhu kan makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, cibiyar kudancin Turai, in ji shi.
Kuma a cewar jami'an, akwai hanyoyin da za a bi da su.
Amurka na da damar, ta hanyar sojin ruwa, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa sun kasance a bude kuma idan ya cancanta, aiwatar da toshewar ruwa, don tabbatar da cewa ba a shigar da makamashin su a kasuwa ba, in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi jawabi ga masu sauraro a taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke kiran kanta "muryar masu amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta dabarun Washington da tattaunawar da Rasha da Iran, ya lura cewa, a zahiri, abu daya ne.
Zaɓin tattalin arziki game da Iran da Rasha shine, kusan, don amfani da kuɗi da maye gurbin man fetur, in ji shi, yana mai cewa Rasha ba ta da "dabara" tare da tattalin arzikin da ke dogara da burbushin mai.
An yi wannan bayanin ne saboda gwamnatin Trump ta shiga cikin wani aiki na kara fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai, da maye gurbin Rasha, wanda shine mafi arha ga masu amfani da Turai.
Don cimma wannan burin, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin Nord Stream 2, wani aikin bututun gas wanda Trump ya ce ya sa Berlin ta zama "kurkuku" ga Moscow.
Moscow ta yi magana sau da yawa cewa Nord Stream 2, bututun gas mai tsada dala biliyan 11, wanda aka tsara don ninka ƙarfin wanda yake akwai zuwa mita biliyan 110 na cubic, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya yi jayayya cewa tsananin adawa da Washington ga aikin yana da dalilai na tattalin arziki kawai kuma misali ne na rashin adalci.
Ina ganin mun yarda cewa ba za a yi amfani da makamashi a matsayin kayan aiki ba, kuma ya kamata a bai wa masu amfani da makamashi damar zaɓar masu samar da su, in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak, bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a watan Satumba a Moscow.
Wannan matakin da Amurka ta dauka ya jawo rashin amincewar Jamus, wadda ta sake tabbatar da cewa ta amince da wannan shiri.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, BDI, ta bukaci Amurka da ta fice daga manufofin samar da makamashi na Tarayyar Turai da kuma yarjejeniyar kasashen biyu da ke tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
Ina ganin cewa wata babbar matsala ce idan wata kasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a cikin samar da makamashi, in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI) bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren za ta yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa a 2020, in ji Sanata daga Massachusetts
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts a ranar Asabar ta ce za ta yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara.
A wani taron gari a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa yana tunanin yin takara.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan na nufin a samu mace a kan mulki", in ji ta, kamar yadda The Hill ta ruwaito.
Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa.
A lokacin taron birnin Warren ya yi magana game da Shugaba Donald Trump, yana cewa yana "kaiwa wannan kasa cikin hanyar da ba daidai ba".
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ta kasance mai tsauraran ra'ayi game da sukar Trump da Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya nada a Kotun Koli.
