Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan sabon tsarin kula da yara
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan yakin shari'a kan sabuwar manufar Amurka da ke hana masu gudun hijira daga 'yan daba ko tashin hankali na cikin gida mafaka.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da na gundumar Columbia a ranar Juma'a sun gabatar da wata takarda ta amicus curiae a Washington don tallafawa wani mai neman mafaka da ya kalubalanci wannan manufar, kamar yadda NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a cikin karar Grace v. Sessions da Kungiyar 'Yancin Jama'a ta Amurka ta gabatar a watan Agusta game da manufar tarayya ba.
Ta ce abokin aikinta  da 'ya'yanta masu cin zarafin 'yan kungiyar  sun ci zarafinta, amma jami'an Amurka sun yi watsi da bukatar da ta yi na karbar mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
