Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da "ta'addanci" ta hanyar "talla"
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wata sanarwa mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka, tana bayyana yadda cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China ke da amfani, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
A ranar Laraba ne Shugaba Donald Trump ya yi magana game da tallan da jaridar China Daily ta biya a jaridar Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan da ta zargi China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta yi watsi da shi.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka shaida wa Reuters cewa wani sabon mataki ne na yakin neman zabe da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
A yayin da gwamnatocin kasashen waje ke yin tallace-tallace don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin yakin cinikayya wanda ya sa suka daidaita harajin da suke bi don shigo da kayayyaki.
Kudaden harajin da China ta saka a farkon yakin cinikin an yi niyyar kai su ne kan masu fitar da kayayyaki zuwa jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican, kamar yadda masana kasar Sin da Amurka suka ce.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
China, Branstad ya rubuta a wata kasida a jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi,  yanzu tana kara girman kai ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace a jaridunmu kyauta. 
A cikin yada farfagandar da take yi, gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da ƙaunatacciyar al'adar Amurka ta 'yancin magana da latsawa ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace a cikin Des Moines Register, Branstad ya rubuta.
A akasin wannan, a cikin jaridar tituna a nan Beijing za ku ga muryoyin 'yan adawa kaɗan kuma ba za ku ga ainihin ra'ayoyin da jama'ar kasar Sin za su iya yi game da matsalar tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin, in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa wani daga cikin manyan jaridu a kasar Sin ya ki bayar da labarin nasa, duk da cewa bai bayyana wane jarida ba.
'Yan Republican na kawar da mata masu zabe a gaban zaben tsakiyar shekara da shari'ar Kavanaugh, masu sharhi sun yi gargadin
Da yake manyan 'yan Republican da dama suna goyon bayan zaben Brett Kavanaugh a Kotun Koli kuma suna tare da shi wajen fuskantar zargin cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun ce za a ga mummunan sakamako, musamman daga mata, a lokacin zaben tsakiyar wa'adi.
An yi ta zanga-zanga sosai a kan wannan batu, kuma 'yan Republican da dama sun riga sun nuna cewa suna son a ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
"Ba za ku iya janye waɗannan abubuwan ba", in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana shakkar cewa takunkumin da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ya yi na neman binciken FBI zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta da shi ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar MoveOn a kasar, kamar yadda jaridar Washington, D.C. ta ruwaito a ranar Juma'a.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a masu zanga-zangar sun sake maimaita taken "Nuwamba tana zuwa!" a yayin zanga-zangarsu a zauren majalisar dattijai, lokacin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da Kwamitin Shari'a suka zabi ci gaba da neman takarar Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, kamar yadda Mic ta ruwaito.
"Jami'an Democrat suna da himma da kuma himma", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai nazarin siyasa mai zaman kansa.
Mutane suna cewa sun riga sun yi tsayi; gaskiya ne.
Amma za su iya zama mafi girma, musamman a tsakanin masu aikin lantarki da ke zaune a unguwannin da ba su da tabbas da kuma matasa masu zabe, tsakanin shekaru 18 zuwa 29, wadanda galibi ba sa jefa kuri'a duk da cewa ba sa son shugaban kasa.
Tun kafin shaidar Ford a bainar jama'a, wanda ya ba da cikakkun bayanai game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i da aka yi wa dan takarar Kotun Koli, manazarta sun yi tunanin cewa za a iya fuskantar mummunan sakamako idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatarwa.
"Game da jam'iyyar Republican, ya zama abin rikicewa", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
Ba wai kawai batun zaben kwamitin ba ne, ko na karshe ko kuma ko za a ajiye Kavanaugh a kan kujerar shugaban kasa, amma kuma yadda 'yan Republican suka gudanar da lamarin da kuma yadda suka bi da shi, in ji Guy Cecil, darektan kungiyar da ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat, Priorities USA.
Ko ta yaya, jama'ar Amirka sun rabu a kan wanda za su amince da shi bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, tare da ƙananan kashi a cikin goyon bayan Kavanaugh.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin ɗari na waɗanda aka yi wa tambayoyi sun gaskata ko kuma sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin ɗari suka ce sun gaskata ko kuma sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce sun yi imani cewa Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka ce haka Ford ya yi.
Bayan da Flake ya nace, FBI ta fara bincike kan zargin da Ford ya yi, da kuma akalla daya daga cikin masu zargin, Deborah Ramirez, kamar yadda The Guardian ta ruwaito.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade lokacin da take da shekaru 17.
Ramirez ta ce wanda ke neman zama a kotun koli ya nuna mata al'aurarsa a wani biki a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai fadi ya shirya fara sabuwar intanet da zata kalubalanci Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai amfani da yanar gizo, yana samar da wata sabuwar hanyar sadarwa da za ta yi gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ya samo asali ne daga dandamali na tushen buɗewa na Berners-Lee Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za su adana bayanan su da abin da mutane za su iya samun dama da kuma abin da bayanai.
A wata hira da Fast Company, Berners-Lee yayi dariya cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
Ya ce, "Ya kamata mu yi hakan yanzu".
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu shagon bayanan sirri na kan layi ko POD.
Za ka iya haɗa da jerin sunayen abokanka, abubuwan da za ka yi, kalandarku, littattafan kiɗa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na kanka da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna cikin burauzar guda a lokaci guda.
Abu na musamman game da kantin sayar da bayanan sirri na kan layi shine cewa mai amfani yana da cikakken zaɓi wanda zai iya samun damar abin da ke ciki.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "Ƙarfafawa ta sirri ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar John Bruce, Shugaba na kamfanin, shine don samar da albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewa masu dacewa don tabbatar da cewa kowa yana iya samun damar Solid.
Kamfanin a halin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓakawa a cikin ma'aikatan da aka ɗauka don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu tsara fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba za su gaya wa Facebook da Google ko su kawo sauyi ba inda tsarin kasuwancin su ya rushe gaba daya cikin dare daya.
Ba ma neman izinin su.
A wani rubutu da ya wallafa a shafin Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da wutar lantarki ta kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon gidan yanar gizo wanda aka gina daga Solid.
A shekara ta 1994 Berners-Lee ya kawo sauyi a yanar gizo lokacin da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watanni da suka gabata Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da bayan ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance Founder da Daraktan World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kwarin gwiwa game da wannan sabon zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
