Mickelson ya yi ritaya a gasar Ryder ta ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai kafa tarihi a ranar Lahadi lokacin da ya buga wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47, amma zai bukaci sake samun lafiya don kauce wa zama wani muhimmin ci gaba.
Mickelson, yana buga gasar shekara biyu a karo na 12 a tarihi, ya samu nasarar zama a kan benci daga kyaftin Jim Furyk domin wasannin hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon zama a tsakiyar wasan kamar yadda ya saba a Amurka, zakaran ya yi aiki a matsayin mai taya murna da kuma aiki a filin wasa, yana fatan gyara abin da ke damunsa.
Tun da yake bai taɓa kasancewa mafi ƙarfi a cikin direbobi ba ko da a lokacin da ya fi tsayi, ɗan shekara 48 ba shi da kyakkyawan zaɓi don Le Golf National mai wahala, inda hanyar da ba ta da kyau ta hukunta kuskuren kuskure.
Kuma idan hanyar da kanta ba ta isa ba, Mickelson, a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi, ya fuskanci zakaran gasar Open na Burtaniya Francesco Molinari, wanda ya yi aiki tare da sabon shiga Tommy Fleetwood don lashe duka wasanninsu huɗu a wannan makon.
Idan Amurkawa, da suka rage maki hudu a wasan su na bana, suka fara wasa da karfi, to wasan Mickelson zai iya zama mai matukar muhimmanci.
Furyk ya nuna cewa yana da tabbaci a kan mutumin da ya aura, amma ba abin da zai faɗa.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci matsayina a yau, ya rungume ni, ya rungume ni kuma ya ce zai kasance a shirye gobe".
Yana da tabbaci sosai a kansa.
Shi Hall of Famer ne kuma ya ƙara da yawa ga ƙungiyoyi a baya, kuma wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban taɓa tunanin yin wasa biyu ba.
Na yi tsammani fiye da haka, amma wannan ita ce hanyar da ta tafi kuma wannan ita ce hanyar da muka yi tunanin ya kamata ya tafi.
Yana son shiga, kamar kowa.
A ranar Lahadi, Mickelson zai doke Nick Faldo a kan mafi yawan wasannin da aka buga a gasar Ryder.
Wannan zai iya nuna ƙarshen aikinsa a gasar Ryder Cup wanda bai taɓa yin daidai da na kansa ba.
Mickelson ya yi wasanni 18 da ya ci, 20 da ya yi asara, kuma bakwai da ya ci, ko da yake Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa a wurin ya kawo dukiya mai yawa ga tawagar.
Yana da ban dariya, mai ba'a, mai hankali, yana son yin izgili da mutane, kuma babban mutum ne da za a samu a cikin ɗakin taro, in ji ta.
Ina kuma ganin 'yan wasan matasa sun ji daɗin fafatawa da shi a wannan makon, abin da ya kasance abin ban sha'awa a gani.
