Wannan shi ne sakon da ya kamata a sanar da 'yan wasan: gobe, dole ne ku fitar da mafi kyawun ku.
Bayan haka, ka manta da abokin aikinka domin shi ma dole ne ya je wurin kuma ya kawo mafi kyawunsa.
Ba kamar Bjorn ba, abokin karawarsa Jim Furyk zai nemi mafi kyawun wasan mutum maimakon na ƙungiya, ban da Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas waɗanda suka sami maki uku daga cikin huɗu.
Furyk ya kasance a bangarorin biyu a manyan wasannin ranar karshe, kasancewar yana cikin tawagar da ta lashe a Brookline kafin ta sha kaye a hannun kungiyar ta Turai ta "Miracle of Medinah".
"Na tuna da kowace kalma", in ji shi a lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da yadda Ben Crenshaw, kyaftin a 1999, ya jagoranci 'yan wasansa a ranar ƙarshe.
