Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
A cewar majiyoyin gwamnati, akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
An katse sadarwa kuma jami'an agaji ba su samu wani bayani daga ofishin Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
Bayan bala'in, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga Palu.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke ƙarshen wani kunkuntar bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi kuma yana da mazaunan kusan 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) na bakin teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar, yanki ne na gudanarwa wanda ke ƙarƙashin lardi, yana da mazauna kusan 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan hanyoyin samun kudin shiga ga tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi da musamman yankin Donggala da ke gabar teku.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na nickel yana da muhimmanci a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani tsunami kuma ya afku a yankin Donggala na yamma a shekarar 1996 inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin tekun Fasifik kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Ga wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi girma a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14 inda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, an yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afku a gabar kudu inda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Wata girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afku kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afku a tsibirin Mentawai, a gabar tekun Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsayin mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
