An kama babban dan Sarah Palin da laifin cin zarafin mata
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi da laifin hari.
A cewar wani rahoto da 'yan sanda suka fitar a ranar Asabar, an kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin gida, da hana bayar da rahoto da kuma tsayayya da kama.
Rahoton ya ce, lokacin da wata abokiyarta ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don bayar da rahoton zargin aikata laifi, ya ƙwace wayar daga hannunta.
An tura Palin zuwa gidan Mat-Su Pretrial Facility kuma an saka masa belin $500, a cewar KTUU.
A cewar gidan talabijin din, ya bayyana a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar kuma ya ce "ba shi da laifi".
Ana iya tuhumar Palin da laifuffuka uku na farko, wato, ɗaurin shekara guda da kuma tara dala 250,000.
An kuma rubuta masa laifi na biyu da za a yi masa daurin yini ɗaya da kuma tara $2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da aka zargi Palin da aikata laifi ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an zarge shi da kai hari ga mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyar, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don bayar da rahoton zargin da ake yi.
Yanzu haka ana sauraron karar a kotun da ke jihar Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da laifin cin zarafin gida, hana bayar da rahoton aikata laifuka da kuma mallakar makami yayin da yake bugu dangane da lamarin.
Budurwarsa ta zarge shi da dūkan fuskarsa.
An soki Sarah Palin daga kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji a shekarar 2016 saboda ta danganta halin tashin hankalin danta da ciwon tashin hankali bayan ya yi aiki a Iraki.
Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia: Daruruwan Sun Mutu
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta haddasa tsunami kuma ta halaka dubban gidaje.
Lantarki da sadarwa sun lalace kuma adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ta afku ne a yankin tsakiyar Sulawesi da ke arewa maso gabashin babban birnin Indonesia, Jakarta.
Wasu bidiyoyi da ke nuna lokacin da jirgin ya faɗi sun bazu a shafukan sada zumunta.
Sa'ad da tsunami ya auku a bakin teku, mutane da yawa sun taru don su yi biki a bakin teku a birnin Palu.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi a yankewa wadanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York hukuncin kisa.
Masu gabatar da kara a New York sun nemi a yankewa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ya kai harin ta'addanci da ya kashe mutane takwas. Wannan hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa wani ba tun shekarar 1953.
Ana zargin Saipov, mai shekara 30, da amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don shiga hanyar keke a kan West Side Highway a yankin Lower Manhattan yana lalata masu tafiya da keke a watan Oktoba.
A karkashin sharuddan da ake bukata na yanke hukuncin kisa a gundumar kudu ta New York, don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi mummunan rauni.
A cewar takardar kotun, duka waɗannan tuhume-tuhume na iya kai ga hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta yanke wa Saipov hukunci kan wasu laifuka 22 da suka hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai tare da aikata laifi, wanda yawanci masu gabatar da kara ke amfani da shi a shari'ar aikata laifuka, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "tsari da kuma tunanin da ya dace", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai shi a matsayin "mummunan, mummunan hali da lalata".
Sanarwar ta farko ta ce "Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da lalacewa, cin mutunci da asarar ga iyalai da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco".
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun shude tun lokacin da gundumar kudancin New York ta fara shari'ar hukuncin kisa.
Mutumin da ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, an tuhume shi da kisan wasu 'yan dillalan miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma an yanke masa hukuncin kisa a watan Satumbar 2009.
An yi hukuncin kisa a ƙarshe a New York a 1953 a cikin shari'ar tarayya na Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, miji da mata da aka zargi da ta'addanci ta hanyar leken asiri kuma aka zarge su da ba da bayanai ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
Ma'aurata Rosenberg sun mutu a kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotu, Saipov, dan kasar Uzbekistan, bai nuna alamar tuba ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya yi alfahari da abin da ya yi a gaban masu binciken.
A cewar tuhumar, Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya yanke shawarar kai harin ne bayan da ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa.
Ya kuma nemi 'yan sanda su rataye tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan tuhume-tuhume 22 da ake tuhumarsa da su.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce "a bayyane yake ya yi takaici" da hukuncin da ake yi.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karɓar laifin da hukuncin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba zai kara tsawaita cutar da wadannan abubuwan suka faru ga duk wanda abin ya shafa", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta bukaci masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
'Yan majalisa na Tory sun ce dole ne Nigel Farage ya jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya sha alwashin "daukar sojojin jama'a" a yau a wani zanga-zanga a taron 'yan Tory.
Lokacin da wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Theresa May ya nuna cewa ya kamata ya kula da tattaunawar da EU, tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar Independence Party na Birtaniya ya ce 'yan siyasa suna bukatar su "ji matsin lamba" daga masu shakka.
A watan Maris, dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya Peter Bone ya ce a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya "za ta riga ta fita daga Turai" idan Farage ya zama Sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da May ke fuskanta wajen kokarin sasanta ra'ayoyin jam'iyyarta da ta rabu biyu, an bayyana su ne a wani zanga-zangar da aka yi a London.
Firaministan kasar na kokarin aiwatar da shirin Chequers a yayin da masu goyon bayan Brexit, da wadanda ke son ci gaba da zama a Turai da kuma kungiyar tarayyar Turai ke kai hare-hare.
Allies sun dage kan ci gaba da kokarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da mummunan haushi da ake samu a tsakanin su, da kuma tilasta wa masu shakkar Yuro da kuma 'yan aiki su zabi tsakanin abin da May ta gabatar da kuma 'hargitsi'.
A wani taron kungiyar Leave Means Leave da aka gudanar a Solihull, Bone ya ce yana son barin Shirin Chequers.
Ya ce ya kamata a bai wa Farage aikin gudanar da shawarwari da Brussels.
"Zamu kasance a waje da Turai a wannan lokacin", in ji shi.
Dan majalisa Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Ina goyon bayan Brexit amma dole ne mu yi watsi da Shirin Chequers".
Da yake bayyana dalilin da ya sa ya ƙi amincewa da Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙi a yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don mu zama bayi ba.
Muna son mu iya yin amfani da dokokinmu a ƙasarmu".
Bone ya yi watsi da ra'ayoyin cewa ra'ayin jama'a zai canza daga zaben 2016: "Tunanin cewa 'yan Burtaniya sun canza ra'ayi kuma suna son zama a Turai ba gaskiya bane".
'Yar majalisar wakilai mai goyon bayan Brexit, Andrea Jenkyns, ta halarci gangamin kuma ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina gaya wa firaministan kasar kawai ya saurari mutane.
Ba a son shirin Chequers a cikin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su yi zabe ba, kuma ba su da goyon bayan jam'iyyarmu da masu fafutukarmu da ke yawo a kan tituna suna neman kuri'u don su zabe mu.
Ka manta da shirin Chequers kuma ka fara sauraro".
A wata sanarwa da ta aikawa May, ta kara da cewa: "Firai ministoci na iya rike mukamin su idan suka cika alkawuransu".
A taron, Farage ya ce 'yan siyasa su iya "jin matsin lamba" idan suna son cin amanar shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
"Yanzu batun amincewa ne tsakanin mu, mutane, da kuma siyasarmu", in ji shi.
"Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu cewa ba za mu bari su yi hakan ba".
A wani sako da ta aika wa masu sauraronta, ta kara da cewa: "Ina so ku nuna cewa siyasarmu tana fuskantar matsin lamba, domin ta kusa cin amanar Brexit.
Muna son mu garzaya da sojojin kasar nan da suka kada kuri'ar neman ficewar Birtaniya, kuma ba za mu tsaya ba har sai mun zama Birtaniya mai zaman kanta, mai zaman kanta da alfahari".
A halin yanzu, masu goyon bayan ci gaba da zama a Turai sun yi zanga-zanga a titunan Birmingham kafin su gudanar da taron sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya sun ja hankalin 'yan Tory kan batun Brexit bayan da aka kafa kungiyar a karshen mako.
Jam'iyyar Labour ta yi ba'a ga 'yan majalisa kan matsalar tsaro da suka samu a wata manhajar jam'iyyar a lokacin da suka bude taron.
"Waɗannan mutane ne da ke cewa za su iya shigar da tsarin IT da duk fasahar da ta dace da yarjejeniyar Canada plus plus, don iyakoki marasa rikici da kuma cinikayya ba tare da iyaka ba a Ireland", in ji shi.
Wannan abin dariya ne.
Babu wata kyakkyawar Brexit", in ji shi.
