Dundee Stars sun tashi daga rashin nasarar da suka sha a wasan Elite League da Belfast Giants ranar Juma'a ta hanyar lashe wasan da suka yi a ranar Asabar 5-3 a Dundee.
Giants sun ci gaba da cin kwallaye biyu a raga daga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun sa 'yan wasan gida su daidaita kafin Dwyer ya mayar da Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya ci wa Dundee kwallo biyu kafin Lukaku Lundvald Nielsen ya ci su.
