A cikin abin da ya kasance farkon lokacin da ya kasance mai ban sha'awa, Sullivan ya dawo da ƙungiyar gida a wasan a minti 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya ba da taimako ga Cownie a minti 15:16.
