Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun ba da gudummawa ga aikin Nielsen wanda ya jagoranci Dundee a karon farko a wasan a ƙarshen rabi na biyu kuma ya ba da nasarar nasarar ƙungiyarsa ta hanyar zura kwallo ta biyar a tsakiyar rabin.
Giants, da suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da suka gabata, za su buga wasansu na gaba a gida a Milton Keynes ranar Juma'a.
Mai kula da jirgin ya mutu don ya ceci daruruwan fasinjoji daga girgizar ƙasa
A Indonesia za a yaba wa wani mai kula da jirgin sama a matsayin gwarzo bayan ya mutu don ya ba da damar jirgin sama da ke dauke da daruruwan mutane ya tashi ya cece su.
Mutane sama da 800 ne suka mutu, wasu kuma sun bata sakamakon wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Juma'a, inda ta haddasa tsunami.
Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta ci gaba da afkawa yankin kuma mutane da dama sun makale a cikin tarkace a garin Palu.
Amma duk da cewa abokan aikinsa sun gudu don ceton rayukansu, Anthonius Gunawan Agung, mai shekara 21, ya kasance a wurinsa a cikin hasumiyar sarrafawa ta Mutiara Sis Al Jufri Airport a Palu, wanda ke rawar jiki cikin tsoro.
Ya so ya tabbata cewa jirgin Batik Air 6321 da ke kan hanyar jirgin ya tashi lafiya.
Saboda haka, ya yi tsalle daga kan hasumiyar sa'ad da yake ganin cewa za ta rushe.
Ya mutu daga baya a asibiti.
Kakakin kamfanin jirgin sama na Air Navigation Indonesia, Yohannes Sirait, ya ce wannan matakin na iya ceton daruruwan rayuka, kamar yadda ABC News ta Australiya ta ruwaito.
Mun shirya wani helikofta daga Balikpapan a Kalimantan don kai shi wani babban asibiti a wani birni.
Abin takaici, ya mutu a safiyar yau kafin jirgin ya isa Palu.
"Wannan labari ne mai matukar bakin ciki a gare mu", in ji shi.
A halin yanzu, hukumomi na fargabar cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu zai kai dubbai, kuma hukumar kula da bala'i ta kasa ta ce an hana shiga garuruwan Donggala, Sigi da Boutong.
"Za a samu karin mutane da suka mutu saboda akwai gawawwaki da yawa a karkashin kasa, kuma ba a iya samun wasu ba", in ji mai magana da yawun hukumar, Sutopo Purwo Nugroho.
Raƙuman ruwa masu tsayi har mita 6 sun lalata Palu, inda za a yi jana'izar jama'a a ranar Lahadi.
Jiragen sama na soji da na kasuwanci suna kawo kayan agaji da abinci.
Risa Kusuma, wata mahaifiya 'yar shekara 35, ta gaya wa Sky News: "A kowace minti, motar asibiti tana kai gawarwaki.
Ruwa mai tsabta yana da ƙarancin gaske.
Ana yin fashi a shagunan sayar da abinci a ko'ina".
Jan Gelfand, shugaban kungiyar agaji ta kasa da kasa a Indonesia, ya shaida wa CNN cewa: "Kungiyar agaji ta kasar Indonesia tana yin duk abin da za ta iya don taimakawa wadanda suka tsira, amma ba mu san abin da za su samu ba.
Yanayin ya riga ya zama abin baƙin ciki, amma zai iya zama mafi muni".
Shugaban kasar Indonesia, Joko Widodo, ya isa Palu a ranar Lahadi kuma ya gaya wa sojojin kasar: "Ina rokon ku da ku yi aiki dare da rana don kammala dukkan ayyukan da suka shafi kwashe mutane.
Shin kun shirya?" in ji CNN.
A lokacin shekarar, girgizar ƙasa ta riga ta afka wa ƙasar Indonesia a Lombok, inda mutane 550 suka mutu.
