Beijing ta mayar da martani a kan wannan matakin a duk lokacin da ta yi hakan, kwanan nan ta saka haraji tsakanin kashi biyar zuwa goma bisa dari a kan kayayyakin Amurka da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
China ta yi alkawarin mayar da martani ga Amurka a kan kai hari, kuma ba zai yiwu ba da babbar tattalin arzikin duniya ta biyu ta koma baya nan ba da jimawa ba.
Don Washington ta yi watsi da bukatarsa, dole ne ta yi biyayya, amma yin biyayya ga Amurka a fili zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi wasa da katunan ta, matsin lamba daga yakin cinikayya da Amurka zai iya shafar kasar Sin a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin kasashen biyu.
Abigail Grace, wata mai bincike a Asiya a Cibiyar Nazarin Sabuwar Tsaro ta Amirka ta ce: "Abin da ya sa za a iya cewa wani mataki na siyasa da Washington ko Beijing suka ɗauka zai iya sa tattalin arziki ya rushe a ƙasashen biyu ya fi abin da aka sani".
Ministan harkokin wajen Syria ya ce Syria a shirye take ta dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta karbi 'yan gudun hijirar da ke dawowa gida kuma tana neman taimako don sake gina kasar da ta lalace sakamakon yakin da aka shafe shekaru bakwai ana yi.
A gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayin kasar na samun sauki.
"Yau yanayin yankin ya fi karko da tsaro saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da farfado da yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don dawo da al'amura cikin sauki.
Yanzu an shirya dukkan abubuwan da za su sa 'yan gudun hijirar su koma kasarsu da son ransu saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki da suka shafi rayuwarsu da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa 'yan Syria sama da miliyan 5.5 sun tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya barke a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a Syria suna bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta amince da taimako don sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya ce ba zai amince da wata tallafi da aka tanada ko kuma ta wasu kasashen da suka goyi bayan tawaye ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ta Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 ta doke ƙungiyar Amurka da ƙimar ƙarshe ta 17.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a wajen Paris, Faransa.
A sakamakon haka, Amirka ta yi rashin nasara sau shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ba a Turai tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kofin lokacin da tawagar Denmark karkashin kyaftin Thomas Bjorn ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin doke Amurka.
Gwarzon Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya a mafi yawan gasar, ya jefa kwallo a cikin ruwa a rami na 16 na par 3 ya ba da nasara ga Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan na Italiya ya yi fice a duk wasanninsa ta hanyar zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka yi rikodin 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
An doke dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth da ci 5 da 4 daga dan wasan Denmark Thorbjorn Olesen na kungiyar Turai.
Dan wasan da ya fi kowa tsayi a duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya mika wuya da 2 da 1 ga dan wasan Ingila Ian Poulter wanda zai iya buga gasar Ryder ta karshe.
Wani tsohon ɗan wasan Ryder Cup, Sergio Garcia na Spain wanda ya yi wasa takwas, ya zama ɗan wasan Turai da ya fi cin nasara a tarihin gasar da maki 25.5.
"Ba na yawan kuka, amma a yau ina kuka sosai.
Shekara ce mai wuya.
Ina godiya ga Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Na yi farin ciki sosai da na sake lashe kofin.
Wannan nasara ce ga tawagar kuma ina farin cikin ba da gudummawata", in ji Garcia bayan nasarar Turai.
Ya mika ragamar ga dan kasarsa John Ram wanda ya doke shahararren dan wasan golf na Amurka Tiger Woods da ci 2 da 1 a wasan bana.
Rahm mai shekara 23 ya ce: "Idan na yi tunanin cewa na girma ina kallon wasanninsa, ina alfahari da na doke Tiger Woods".
Woods ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu da ya buga a Faransa kuma yanzu ya yi nasara a gasar Ryder Cup 13 da 21 da kuma 3 da aka yi.
Wannan adadi ne mai ban mamaki idan aka yi la'akari da cewa shi ne daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa a duk lokacin da ya lashe manyan wasanni 14, wanda Jack Nicklaus ne kawai ya fi nasara.
Kungiyar Amurka ta shafe tsawon karshen mako tana neman hanyoyin da za su bi, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, wadanda suka buga wasan golf na musamman a duk gasar.
Kyaftin na Amirka Jim Furyk ya ce bayan wasan da tawagarsa ta yi da bai dace ba: "Ina alfahari da waɗannan yara domin sun yi yaƙi.
A wani lokaci a safiyar yau, mun matsa wa tawagar Turai.
Mun yi watsi da wannan zarafi.
Na gode wa Thomas.
Shi babban kyaftin ne.
Dukkan 'yan wasansa 12 sun yi aiki sosai.
Zan yi aiki tare da PGA na Amurka da kuma kwamitin gasar Ryder kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina son waɗannan yara 12 kuma ina alfahari da kasancewa kyaftininsu.
Mun yi iya ƙoƙarinmu.
Amma sun yi wasa fiye da mu".
Sabuntawa game da ruwan tsufana: Rashin hankali yana raguwa a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da Hukumar Kifi da Daji ta Florida ta bayar ya nuna cewa yawan ruwan teku ya ragu a yankunan da ke yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, yanayin fure-fure, wanda ke nuna raguwar taro, yana bayyane a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier.
Ruwan ruwan sama mai ruwan kasa yana da nisan mil 130 daga arewacin Pinellas County zuwa kudancin Lee County.
An samu wasu wurare da ke da nisan mil 10 daga garin Hillsborough amma an samu wasu wurare da ba su da yawa kamar yadda aka samu a makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga ruwan sama a yankin Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata an samu matsakaicin taro a cikin Pinellas County ko kuma a gabar tekun, daga ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a cikin Hillsborough County, daga ƙananan taro zuwa babban taro a cikin Manatee County, daga ƙananan taro zuwa babban taro a cikin Sarasota County ko a gabar tekun, daga ƙananan taro zuwa matsakaici a cikin Charlotte County, daga ƙananan taro zuwa babban taro a cikin Lee County ko a gabar tekun, da ƙananan taro a cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahoton ciwon numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Amma a makon da ya gabata, babu wani mutum da ya kamu da cutar a arewa maso yammacin Florida.
